Using web interface or ide plugin, authenticated developer or service provider uploads a previously prepared file to the Ustore, and then the system checks the file for correctness using built-in tools. According to the metadata of the service, and the properties of the service provider or the developer (they may be declared as trusted), the successfully checked service is published, or sent to an administrator for approval.
